data.description: This stunning home features 4 spacious bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms. As you approach the property, you are immediately captivated by its incredible curb appeal. Upon entering, you are greeted by the grandeur of tall ceilings and an abundance of natural light streaming in from all angles, creating an inviting and warm ambiance. The combination of carpet and ceramic tile flooring adds a touch of sophistication while ensuring comfort throughout the home. Hosting formal gatherings is a pleasure in the expansive dining room, offering ample space for entertaining family and friends. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring stainless steel appliances, and exquisite granite countertops. Retreat to the luxurious primary bedroom located on the main floor, where tall ceilings and ample natural light create a serene and tranquil atmosphere. The en-suite primary bathroom, which offers a true haven for relaxation. Featuring double vanities, a large garden tub, a separate walk-in shower, and a generously sized walk-in closet, this spa-like retreat is the epitome of comfort and style. In addition to the primary bedroom, the home offers three additional bedrooms, each offering its own unique charm. A game room/media room provides fantastic areas for entertainment, creating a haven for family and friends to gather and enjoy their favorite activities. This home is zoned into the prestigious NISD and is surrounded by tons of shopping and dining options.
